# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. Copy this file to your project root:
#    cp .env.template .env
#
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual configuration:
#    - XYOPS_API_KEY: Get from xyOps admin panel
#    - SERVICENOW_USER/PASSWORD: Your ServiceNow credentials
#    - N8N_WEBHOOK_TOKEN: Generate a secure token
#    - N8N_HMAC_SECRET: Generate a secure secret
#
# 3. n8n is enabled by default (ENABLE_N8N=true).
#    Set ENABLE_N8N=false to fall back to direct xyOps calls.
#    Import N8N/n8n_master_orchestrator.json into n8n and activate it.
#
# 4. Ensure .env is in .gitignore (included in this repo)
#
# 4. Load environment variables:
#    - Docker Compose: Reads .env automatically
#    - Local development: source .env
#
# 5. Never commit .env to version control
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
